text: DWNA-TV, channel 22, is a television station of Philippine television network TV5. Its transmitter is located at Maharlika Highway, Naga, Camarines Sur. TV5 Naga started its official broadcast in 2016. Prior to this, TV5 Naga was on Channel 5 (DZGB-TV) as an affiliate of PBN Broadcasting Network from 1995 to 2016. ==Rebroadcast== {| class="wikitable" ! Station ! Transmitter Location ! Channels !
